Caules saepe spithamales et ultra, erecti, apice nutantes v. prostrati, aliquantulum compressi, glabre- scentes v. rarius ex parte glanduloso-pubescentes Folia semiteretia, lineari- filiformia, apice subulata, interdum mucronata, laete virentia, glabrescentia, internodiis raro longiora. Stipulae breves, late ovatae, breviter acuminatae, fere integrae parum nitidae. Pedimculi floriferi fere omnes foliis destituti, infimi interdum foliis fulti, demum capsula vix duplo longiores. Sepala acuminata, margine anguste v. latius scarioso. Petala late ovata, ob— tusa, calycem fere aequantia, albida, apice rosea. Capsula magna, ea- lyce fere duplo longior, ovata, obtusa. Semina rufofusca, laevia, compla- nata, rotundata, margine parum elevato praedita, saepissime late alata (v. v. sp. et cult).
